text: The Aero & Tech Nexth is an Italian Ultralight aircraft. It was introduced in 2011. It uses a Rotax 912ULS engine. The aircraft is still in production. == Performance == * Maximum speed: 240 km/h (150 mph, 130 kn) * Cruise speed: 225 km/h (140 mph, 121 kn) Category:Italian aircraft
title: Aero & Tech Nexth
